1 bag herbs
1 packet capers
1 packet the everything bagel
1 tub cream cheese
1 packet Akaroa Cold Smoked Salmon

Finely chop chives.

Halve the everything bagels. Toast or grill to your liking.

Transfer toasted bagels to plates. Spread cream cheese over bagel halves. Top with Akaroa cold smoked salmon, chives and capers. Season with salt and pepper.